{"title":"在田野（三首）","authors":["奕林"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":12,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在田野（三首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奕　林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"油菜花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一大片望不到边的油菜花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金黄，金黄，云霞般明丽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳一定是在春天孕育，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也一定会从这里升起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看！远处跃出煊红的一点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳刚跳上地平线的台阶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"移过来了，移过来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成清晰的图象："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却是个红衣服的小村姑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她低着头，专心地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛在寻找着什么，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手臂挽着盛草的篮子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她并不觉得自己的美丽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也没注意路人惊羡的唏嘘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒲公英"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻地一鼓腮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风将你带上天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成熟了的，自然要离开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又何必苦苦地拖缠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我曾嫉妒过风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫉妒过云彩；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中有很多很多的泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你能理解我的情感？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞去吧，飞去吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既然你已不再留恋；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白色的小鸟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是应属于永恒的蓝天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为没有水份，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋风乍起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就呈晶亮晶亮的黄色。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也因为没有水份，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落在地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能发出金属的脆响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金黄的色彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金属的脆响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳贵重的奖赠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的感情掺过水份吗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻浮的云不知，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好事的风也不知，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有深沉的大地知道。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}